                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-sergeant G</hi> 22.) I produce a certificate of the prisoner Owen's former conviction at this Court—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted</hi> 4<hi rend="italic">th April</hi>, 1842, <hi rend="italic">and confined three months</hi>)—he is the person.</p>
